{"tid":297904,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果香港失去Factwire，你地甘心嗎？","createTime":"2017-06-26T00:05:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-29T23:50:28.000Z","uid":9348,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8f258609409dfb8b6f64809c244017c7073516a1","tid":297904,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T00:05:48.000Z","msg":"2015年7月，香港人集資創辦新聞通訊社FactWire。當時FactWire《傳真社》還未有記者團隊，也未見成績，只有一個響亮的宣言 - 本著公眾利益監察權貴，以客觀證據報道真相。<br />\n​<br />\n結果《傳真社》從3,300名市民手上募得470萬港元始創資金，成為亞洲區至今最成功的新聞眾籌案例。<br />\n​<br />\n《傳真社》及後通過公開招募從約300名應徵者中挑選了10人組成編採團隊，包括4名調查記者、2名新聞記者、2名資料搜集員及2名實習記者，並在2016年3月1日正式運作。這個細小的編採團隊並非業界新丁，他們來自本港多家新聞機構，包括《香港電台》、《明報》、《東方日報》、《星島日報》、《蘋果日報》和《壹週刊》。他們經驗豐富，本有大樹護蔭，但都受到感召而離開安定的崗位，加入《傳真社》的調查報道行列。<br />\n​<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">這裡可以「正常地做新聞 」</span><br />\n​<br />\n《傳真社》有別於他們服務過的新聞機構。這裡沒有大商家的水喉，沒有百年老店的招牌，沒有數百人的編採團隊，但這裡有一樣東西叫他們不再回頭，就是揭露真相的自由。全因《傳真社》沒有老闆，沒有廣告商，這裡可以「正常地做新聞 」。<br />\n​<br />\n要維持這種「自由 」和「正常」，必須讓《傳真社》保持獨立，具備穩健和獨立的財政狀況。去年眾籌所得的470萬港元，扣除眾籌平台FringeBacker百分之五收費和信用卡捐款的手續費，最後實得資金為430萬港元。新聞部成立時動用了50萬港元支付辦公室租金上期按金和裝修，以及購買設備。目前每月基本開支為30萬港元（包括薪金及租金，不包括外出採訪、查冊等開支）。<br />\n​<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">送給自己和下一代的禮物</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n​<br />\n今天《傳真社》不再是一個夢想。我們的調查報道獲數以百家本地及海外媒體採用，發揮了傳媒應有的監察力量，每次都迫使有所隱瞞的機構與官員面對公眾，交代事件。由此可見，一家獨立持平、具公信力、以事實為基石的新聞機構，對現時香港有重要的價值。<br />\n​<br />\n捐一年報紙費就足以改變一切<br />\n​<br />\n正當大眾對熟悉的新聞媒體逐漸變得陌生，香港人卻讓《傳真社》奇蹟般誕生並逐步建立公信力。這是港人送給自己和下一代的禮物。《傳真社》決定進行一次眾籌，目標是籌得最少兩年的營運經費。<br />\n​<br />\n公信力是新聞工作的基石，《傳真社》不急於求成，堅持以真憑實據，公正持平的調查報道取信於公眾，讓時間和歷史證明你今天對《傳真社》的信任和託付是對的。<br />\n​<br />\n容我們重申，《傳真社》屬非牟利公共新聞機構，所有公眾捐款和未來營運收入全部用於新聞編採工作。<br />\n <br />\n我們希望能號召5,000人捐出一年的報紙費給《傳真社》，按一份報章每天7元計算，一共是2,555元。<br />\n​<br />\n如果你是「Like」《傳真社》面書的其中一人，希望你把「Like」變成一年的捐款，讓「Like」成為改變一切的力量。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.factwire.org/backus\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.factwire.org%2Fbackus&d=cqr16t5r9tUJDj39CKmzKl0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=4896b0e5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.factwire.org/backus</a>"},{"pid":"9d8304601e6a28bf6cf6cefe46cf7cbc95ed6e00","tid":297904,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T00:12:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"386978de26434ca6f2390d079350023b30fe0b39","tid":297904,"uid":102132,"like":0,"dislike":22,"score":-22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T00:14:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d174eac7c1f48abd757d17b6e39d2b7bc9ceb8ac","tid":297904,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T00:16:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8242d65154e12d4ebd3eb79df7394879986868b5","tid":297904,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T00:43:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3244f5716619df8c0de4c6d945b291377d99070","tid":297904,"uid":42921,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T00:46:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留返比左膠捐<br />\n佢地大撚把錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nOn9, factwire 都屌"},{"pid":"b2fc5b9d91dd64881074f303c134807feebdbc8a","tid":297904,"uid":9348,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T01:14:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>留返比左膠捐<br />\n佢地大撚把錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nOn9, factwire 都屌</blockquote><br />\n波台狗黎既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b37e4af682c512a4b46019a9490847f5ce34e211","tid":297904,"uid":38472,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T01:31:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留返比左膠捐<br />\n佢地大撚把錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n波台多五毛or假膠，垃圾台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c64d09b1bbef6825b3350cf1786be9d1ee025abf","tid":297904,"uid":498,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T01:32:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留返比左膠捐<br />\n佢地大撚把錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人渣敗類"},{"pid":"31c174345b2d8dd932de64e9beb88e01b7304a2c","tid":297904,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T01:33:54.000Z","msg":"會捐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c5fff4c626c9357ed3ee7073049095d0d667703","tid":297904,"uid":96964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T01:37:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceb7f66e3009e8e04e530eb06a179dde3c128425","tid":297904,"uid":44358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T01:42:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留返比左膠捐<br />\n佢地大撚把錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你都係捐返入你老母個閪啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f52b35399c0fd890f6c7c614f1f708bed4715ccb","tid":297904,"uid":53687,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T01:43:04.000Z","msg":"支持，報導夠深入持平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d1b22f4be1e060b12ae3fd58069da7a0b2d290f","tid":297904,"uid":9348,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T04:03:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"429dfa4514e4628733250d5ef7407a6492931c38","tid":297904,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T04:06:24.000Z","msg":"我記得之前評論過FACTWIRE雖好, 但佢個BUSINESS MODEL唔健康<br />\n<br />\n有堆柒頭衝出黎話, 今年FACTWIRE開始向轉載新聞既媒體收錢, <br />\n<br />\n就無晒財政問題架啦<br />\n<br />\n依家又要籌？<br />\n<br />\n堆柒頭依家去左邊, 潛水?"},{"pid":"7a262d92b1eb44c00e8467aa2b51e5c5bdc73960","tid":297904,"uid":9348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T04:07:40.000Z","msg":"感激各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 眾籌之外都希望大家不忘爆料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11330e99d3427d44d9ee39321be87d372d3ffd92","tid":297904,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T04:15:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b426c107ede4f498a89271a16ce7bc1ed72067e","tid":297904,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T05:02:06.000Z","msg":"Factwire真係搵命博"},{"pid":"bd2b40c6ab7a89e6f8d40debc918d1a8220c439a","tid":297904,"uid":64576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T05:10:49.000Z","msg":"巴打<br />\n不如研究下的士狗同uber"},{"pid":"492b4a90e93b9c67a51af254f52fbbe21bde71ce","tid":297904,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T05:15:23.000Z","msg":"捐咗500，加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e37ada8944d2963b575292954ff4ea64872e00c","tid":297904,"uid":45213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T05:31:53.000Z","msg":"課左一千俾大亨同佢老婆去旅遊，不了"},{"pid":"bc27aca5f093d4cbd325cab9d13778122ea2a76c","tid":297904,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T14:27:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e8dc219d1caf467c62cebc78ac0549793bac28a","tid":297904,"uid":2357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T14:32:44.000Z","msg":"唔係一盤生意咁run,難"},{"pid":"25898fcafd770253f79c43eaf3faf5da5bd02ce1","tid":297904,"uid":37030,"like":0,"